				<p class="post-info">Posted in <a href="http://relishingit.com/category/salad/" title="View all posts in Salad" rel="category tag">Salad</a> | Tagged <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/balsamic-vinegar/" rel="tag">Balsamic Vinegar</a>, <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/honey/" rel="tag">Honey</a>, <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/mint/" rel="tag">Mint</a>, <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/oranges/" rel="tag">Oranges</a>, <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/roasted-beets/" rel="tag">Roasted Beets</a>, <a href="http://relishingit.com/tag/salad/" rel="tag">Salad</a> | <a href="http://relishingit.com/2012/03/28/roasted-beets-with-orange-and-mint/#comments" title="Comment on Roasted Beets with Orange and&nbsp;Mint">12 Comments &#187;</a></p>
